{
  "texts": [
    "Dengue fever, despite being a neglected tropical disease, imposes substantial public health and economic consequences.",
    "Our ensemble model offers a timely and effective forecasting system to empower local governments.",
    "The remaining part of the paper is structured as follows.",
    "Section \"Materials and methods\" introduces the methodology proposed and the data used in section \"Results\" we present the results obtained with the proposed method, tested on different scenarios.",
    "In section \"Discussion\" we discuss the limitations and advantages of our approach."
  ]
}